title: HBO's 'Silicon Valley' returns April 23rd
text:
HBO's 'Silicon Valley' returns April 23rd An anticipated 'Game of Thrones' delay won't stop Pied Piper. Share Save 
HBO's tech-industry satire Silicon Valley will return for its fourth season on April 24th . Despite its usual lead-in Game of Thrones likely getting a late start on its seventh season, Pied Piper & Co. are returning in their usual spring window. We don't have any details on what they're getting up to over the next ten episodes or even a teaser trailer, but we did get a quick visit with some of the cast members via Instagram . A video posted by Thomas Middleditch (@tombini) on Feb 10, 2017 at 10:04am PST
